            "id": 1,
            "name": "technology"
        }

# Group Comment

Resource Defination

    {
        "id": "number",
        "idea_id": "number",
        "commenter_id": "number",
        "time": "datetime",
        "content": "string"
    }

## /api/ideas/{idea_id}/comments

### GET

Get all comments (of an idea).

+ Parameters

    + idea_id: `1` (number, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "id": 1,
                "idea_id": 1,
                "commenter_id": 1,
                "time": 2015-11-23 15:00:00 (Not sure),
                "content": "This idea is fantastic"
            }
        ]

### POST

Create a comment.

+ Parameters

    + idea_id: `1` (number, required)

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "commenter_id": 1,
            "time": 2015-11-23 15:00:00 (Not sure),
            "content": "This idea is fantastic"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "idea_id": 1,
            "commenter_id": 1,
            "time": 2015-11-23 15:00:00 (Not sure),
            "content": "This idea is fantastic"
        }
        
## /api/ideas/{idea_id}/comments/{id}

### GET

Get the comment.

+ Parameters

    + idea_id: `1` (number, required)
    + id: `1` (number, required)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "idea_id": 1,
            "commenter_id": 1,
            "time": 2015-11-23 15:00:00 (Not sure),
            "content": "This idea is fantastic"
        }

